<div class="thumb tright" style="width:302px;">
<div class="rounders" style="width:300px;height:224px"><a class="image" title="Macaroni &amp; Cheese 6930.jpg" href="/Image:Macaroni-%26-Cheese-6930.jpg"><img alt="Make Old Style Macaroni and Cheese" src="http://pad3.whstatic.com/images/thumb/a/ad/Macaroni-%26-Cheese-6930.jpg/300px-Macaroni-%26-Cheese-6930.jpg" width="300" height="224" border="0" class="mwimage101" /></a>
