</div></div><a name="Ingredients"></a></p>
</div>
<h2><a href="/index.php?title=Make-Old-Style-Macaroni-and-Cheese&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1" title="Edit section: Ingredients" id="gatEditSection" class="button button52 editsection" onmouseover="button_swap(this);" onmouseout="button_unswap(this);" onclick="gatTrack(gatUser,'Edit','Edit_section');">edit</a> <span>Ingredients</span></h2>
<div id="ingredients" class='article_inner editable'>
<p>Serves 4.</p>
<ul>
<li>1 pound elbow pasta</li>
<li>1/2 cup butter (1 stick)</li>
<li>1/2 cup flour</li>
<li>4 cups milk</li>
<li>1/2 t. dried mustard or up to 1 tsp. Dijon mustard (optional)</li>
<li>A few shakes of cayenne pepper (optional)</li>
<li>10 to 12 ounces extra sharp cheddar</li>
<li>1/2 t. salt (to taste)</li>
<li><a href="/Make-Buttered-Crumbs" title="Make Buttered Crumbs">buttered breadcrumbs</a> (optional)</li>
</ul>
<p><br />
300 g macaroni 50 g butter 50 g flour 600 ml milk 350 g grated cheese</p>
<p><a name="Steps"></a></p>
</div>
<h2><a href="/index.php?title=Make-Old-Style-Macaroni-and-Cheese&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2" title="Edit section: Steps" id="gatEditSection" class="button button52 editsection" onmouseover="button_swap(this);" onmouseout="button_unswap(this);" onclick="gatTrack(gatUser,'Edit','Edit_section');">edit</a> <span>Steps</span></h2>
<div id="steps" class='editable'>
<ol class="steps_list_2">
<li><div class="step_num">1</div><b class='whb'>Heat the milk (on the stove or in the microwave), but don't let it boil</b>. Keep it warm.<div class='wh_ad'>
<div class='wh_ad_inner'>
<script type="text/javascript"><!--

if (!gHideAds) {
    google_max_num_ads = '1';
} 
xchannels = ""; 

function google_ad_request_done(google_ads) {
	var i;
	if (google_ads.length == 0) { return; }
padding = "";
	s = '<div class="adunit adunitp0"><div id="adunit1" ' + adPadding + '><p style="margin:0 0 5px 0; padding:0; font-size:1em;"><a href="'
